@MasterBackup_API_HostAddress = https://localhost:7001
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### Registrar nuevo tenant y admin
POST {{MasterBackup_API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@ejemplo.com",
  "password": "Password123",
  "firstName": "Juan",
  "lastName": "Pérez",
  "tenantName": "Mi Empresa",
  "subdomain": "miempresa",
  "enableTwoFactor": false
}

### Login sin 2FA
POST {{MasterBackup_API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@ejemplo.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### Login con 2FA
POST {{MasterBackup_API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@ejemplo.com",
  "password": "Password123",
  "twoFactorCode": "123456"
}

### Obtener información del usuario actual
GET {{MasterBackup_API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Habilitar 2FA
POST {{MasterBackup_API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/enable-2fa
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Deshabilitar 2FA
POST {{MasterBackup_API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/disable-2fa
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Solicitar recuperación de contraseña
POST {{MasterBackup_API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@ejemplo.com"
}

### Restablecer contraseña
POST {{MasterBackup_API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@ejemplo.com",
  "token": "reset-token-from-email",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword123"
}

### Invitar usuario (solo Admin)
POST {{MasterBackup_API_HostAddress}}/api/users/invite
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario@ejemplo.com",
  "role": "User"
}

### Aceptar invitación
POST {{MasterBackup_API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/accept-invitation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "invitation-token-from-email",
  "password": "Password123",
  "firstName": "María",
  "lastName": "García",
  "enableTwoFactor": false
}

